                         CONTINUE                                
        ELSE             EXIT PERFORM                            
        END-IF                          *>20111019               
     END-PERFORM.                                                
     IF W-I > 5                  DISPLAY CASE-ID "OK"            
        ELSE                     DISPLAY CASE-ID "NG"            
     END-IF.                                                     
